<h3><span id="Publishers.27_series"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Publishers'_series">Publishers' series</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=History_of_books&amp;action=edit&amp;section=46" title="Edit section: Publishers&#039; series">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
